Fun√ß√£o para as an√°lises gr√°ficas

diag_fun <- function(data, mapping, hist=list(), ...){
  
  X = eval_data_col(data, mapping$x)
  mn = mean(X)
  s = sd(X)
  
  ggplot(data, mapping) + 
    do.call(function(...) geom_histogram(aes(y =..density..), ...), hist) +
    stat_function(fun = dnorm, args = list(mean = mn, sd = s), ...)
}
